isted are old stale sub-agents from the previous session.\\n\\nI should note this in the heartbeat state. But for now — HEARTBEAT_OK since it's just echoing heartbeats and not causing any harm. The pipeline is healthy.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"HEARTBEAT_OK\\n\\n*QLHV group session (-5163901258) chỉ đang echo heartbeat, không có task thực. Pipeline healthy.*\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 826,\n            \"output\": 162,\n            \"totalTokens\": 145940,\n            \"cacheRead\": 143831,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 1121,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776166719638,\n          \"responseId\": \"062d5a4152722622bc8ee732381bbb32\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"56198dd5\",\n            \"seq\": 1267\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258\",\n      \"kind\": \"group\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:-5163901258\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776166577770,\n      \"sessionId\": \"8e0cb2bc-8245-4c89-bc2c-e3cca2257d0f\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 94652,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776163408296,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776163783190,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 8014,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n 