ống DÙNG CHUNG database:**\n\n```\nDTLX (MASTER) ─────────────────── QLHV (SUBSYSTEM)\n   Hệ thống chính                    Tách ra cho THẦY/GV\n   Ban giám đốc, Sales, Admin        Giáo viên quản lý HV\n        │                                 │\n        └──────── SHARED MONGODB ────────┘\n              103.253.21.98:27017\n```\n\n**→ QLHV phải đồng bộ dữ liệu với DTLX luôn luôn.**\n**→ Khi dev QLHV, phải HIỂU DTLX schema vì cùng DB.**\n\n## Project Identity\n- **DTLX Name**: AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe) — MASTER\n- **QLHV Name**: AHV QLHV (Quản Lý Học Viên) — SUBSYSTEM\n- **Telegram\n\nSource: memory/dtlx-context.md#L1-L46","source":"memory","citation":"memory/dtlx-context.md#L1-L46","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"89ccf26b7040ce021e9526b7117935aab4b4418e9afc2e7f38a71f602ec196dd","path":"memory/2026-04-14.md","startLine":21,"endLine":41,"score":0.7222095086420897,"textScore":0.7222095086420897,"snippet":"3. `/users/sales/counter` → 500: `docCounter[0] || {}` for empty aggregate\n  4. `/lessons/detail-by-date` → server crash: route reorder (`/:id` catchall moved after specific routes)\n  5. `/teacher-infos` → 404: added `router.get('/')` route\n\n## 08:00 UTC — DTLX BE Full API Test Results (79 endpoints)\n- **Tested:** 79 endpoints via Python script\n- **Results:** ✅ 67 OK | ⚠️ 11 WARN | ❌ 0 ERR\n- **WARNs (expected behavior, not bugs):** change-password (400 missing fields), refetch-token (403 expired), users/students (404 no data), users/teachers (404 no data), exam-results/me (404 no data), conventions (404 POST-only module), imports (404 POST-only module), student/teacher-comments (400 missin\n\nSource: memory/2026-04-14.md#L21-L41","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-04-14.md#L21-L41","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"6d33dcbcde98902d6f184f316670fd98825cd1bfa92d0d558a8ab236984c0dee","path":"memory/dtlx-context.md","startLine":38,"endLine":60,"score":0.7172343687149557,"textScore":0.7172343687149557,"snippet":"### Bộ 2: Ecosystem (ahv-qlhv/*) — ĐANG DEV TRONG SESSION NÀ